## Distribution Readiness

### Before Submission

- [ ] App icon at all required sizes
- [ ] Splash/launch screen (not blank white)
- [ ] Screenshots for all required device sizes
- [ ] Privacy policy URL
- [ ] Terms of service URL
- [ ] App description (clear, no keyword stuffing)
- [ ] Permissions explained (camera, location, notifications - justified in review notes)
- [ ] No test/debug data visible
- [ ] No placeholder text or images
- [ ] Crash-free rate above 99%
- [ ] Works without network (graceful degradation)
- [ ] Deep links tested
- [ ] Push notifications tested on real device
- [ ] Theme variants tested (if app supports multiple themes)
- [ ] Accessibility basics: VoiceOver/TalkBack navigation works
